<LocalizedProperties><Language>en</Language><Title>Security Update for Windows Vista (KB942831)</Title><Description>A security issue has been identified in Windows Internet Information Services (IIS) that could allow an attacker to remotely compromise your Windows-based system and gain control over it. You can help protect your computer by installing this update from Microsoft. After you install this item, you may have to restart your computer.</Description><UninstallNotes>This software update can be removed by selecting View installed updates in the Programs and Features Control Panel.</UninstallNotes><MoreInfoUrl>http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=106361</MoreInfoUrl><SupportUrl>http://support.microsoft.com</SupportUrl></LocalizedProperties>